summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of North and West Seventy-sixth Street form Greeenwood Avenue to Eighth Avenue N.W. in the City of Seattle, by constructing water mains under Ordinance No. 16197, creating Local Improvement District No. 1515 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
